<item>
            <title>[HBASE-10688] Add a draining_node script to manage nodes in draining mode</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-10688</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As per parent issue, our support for graceful stop and node decommissioning can be improved a lot. However, until we fix it for good, we can add a draining_node script to manage the nodes in draining mode in zk. &lt;/p&gt;
